Mozambique settlements locations

settlements.Rd

Mozambique settlements locations

settlements

Format

A SpatialPointsDataFrame object containing settlements locations of Mozambique

| Variables | Description | | OBJECTID | Object identifier | | FID_1 | Feature identifier | | Sett_Name | Settlement name | | F_CLASS | Feature class | | F_DESIG | Feature designation | | ADM1_Old | Administrative level 1 name - old |

Source

https://data.humdata.org/dataset/mozambique-settlement-shapefiles

Examples

settlements
#> class       : SpatialPointsDataFrame 
#> features    : 24602 
#> extent      : 30.2313, 40.8344, -26.8511, -10.5427  (xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax)
#> crs         : +proj=longlat +datum=WGS84 +no_defs 
#> variables   : 23
#> names       : OBJECTID, FID_1,  Sett_Name, F_CLASS, F_DESIG,     ADM1_Old,     ADM2_Old,    Country, ISO3,    ADM1_Name, ADM1_Code, ADM1_ID,    ADM2_Name, ADM2_Code, ADM2_ID, ... 
#> min values  :        1,     0, 7 de Abril,       P,     PPL, Cabo Delgado, Alto Molocue, Mozambique,  MOZ, Cabo Delgado,      MZ01,      01, Alto Molocue,   MZ01001,     001, ... 
#> max values  :     9999,  9999,       Zuze,       P,     PPL,     Zambezia,        Zumbu, Mozambique,  MOZ,     Zambezia,      MZ10,      10,        Zumbu,   MZ10128,     128, ...
